#Text=A SINGLE TOOTH FROM 58., A COMPLETE SET
#Text=“I, Joseph Rogers, aged 64, residing at Silvertown, North Woolwich, do hereby testify to the extreme value of Mr.
#Text=Cooper’s preparation for preventing baldness and retoring the hair.

#Text=I have ©special pleasure in recommending it, for, having been bald during twelve years, my hair has by its means been restored to me of a luxuriant growth and of a colour far preferable to its former hue.
